B.QF=new A.eM("Defer the notification preferences screen to post-onboarding","Stakeholders wanted it up front. We argued it added friction before users had context to make meaningful choices.","Shipped with compromise: one opt-in toggle at step one, full settings deferred. Both sides partially satisfied.",B.nt)
B.QH=new A.eM("Introduced an inline confirmation pattern instead of a modal","Modals were blocking flow and causing accidental dismissal on mobile. Inline felt lower stakes.","Reduced perceived friction but required more implementation effort than estimated. Worth it for mobile, borderline on desktop.",B.jO)
B.QD=new A.eM("Prioritised loading skeletons over a global spinner","Global spinners gave no spatial context. Skeletons reduced perceived wait time in earlier usability tests.","Users reported the interface felt faster. Engineering flagged complexity of per-component skeleton states.",B.h9)
